CUDA (with multi GPU support) and openmp aware routines for Cartesian 1-D, 2-D, and 3-D grids with focus on solving linear/non-linear Schrodinger equation.

See documentation and license information under doc/ directory.

Libgrid was written by Jussi Eloranta (eloranta@aa6kj.hopto.org) with contributions from Lauri Lehtovaara and David Mateo.

This project was partly funded by National Science Foundation grants CHE-0949057, CHE-1262306 and DMR-1205734. For license information see doc/GPL.txt .
